function getCookie(cname) {
    var name = cname + "=";
    var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
    var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
    for(var i = 0; i <ca.length; i++) {
        var c = ca[i];
        while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
            c = c.substring(1);
        }
        if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
            return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
        }
    }
    return "";
}

		<script>
var navbar = document.getElementById("navbar");
var sticky = navbar.offsetTop;

function myFunction() {
  if (window.pageYOffset >= sticky) {
    navbar.classList.add("sticky")
  } else {
    navbar.classList.remove("sticky");
  }
}


 
	 	
	 	function viewDropDownChangee()
	 	{
	 	    var data_view1=document.getElementById("data_view").value.toLowerCase().trim(); 
	 	    var form_view1=document.getElementById("charts_form").action.toLowerCase().trim(); 
	 	   
	 	    //alert(data_view1 + " " + form_view1 );
	 	    if(data_view1==1)
	 	    {
	 	        form_view1 = form_view1.replace("charts", "gold/history");
	 	    }
	 	    else
	 	    if(data_view1==2)
	 	    {
	 	        form_view1 = form_view1.replace("gold/history", "charts");
	 	    }
	 	    
	 	     document.getElementById('charts_form').action =form_view1;

	 	}
